{
  "id": "adv_event_2201_02_01",
  "title": "お正月 2021",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_02_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "あっ！　来た来た！\n{user}さん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! {user}-san‚ you're here!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 3.6382766724,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_02_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "みんなで挨拶したくて\n待ってたんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've been waiting to greet everyone!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.8333333333,
      "endTime": 6.8326302846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_02_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "えーっと、明けまして\nおめでとうございます！\nふつつか者ですが、今年も\nよろしくお願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ Happy New Year!\nI'm just a humble person‚ but please take care of me this year too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.0333333333,
      "endTime": 14.4492290814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_02_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、さくらちゃん\nそれ使いどころが違うわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ Sakura-chan‚ you're using it in the wrong context.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.6333333333,
      "endTime": 19.240974839499998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_02_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "ふつつか者ですが……\n今年もよろしく、です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm just a humble person…\nPlease take care of me this year too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.4333333333,
      "endTime": 24.7115418751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_02_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "もう雫ちゃん\n真似しちゃダメっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruka-chan‚ don't copy me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.9,
      "endTime": 28.055691671399998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_02_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "何はともあれ\n今年も私達のことお願いね！\n{user}君！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ please take care of us this year too!\n{user}!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.5,
      "endTime": 34.157392311100004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_02_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ\n賑やかで楽しい新年だね\n私はみんなと\nいい年にしたいなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehehe‚ it's a lively and enjoyable New Year.\nI want to have a great year with everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.3666666667,
      "endTime": 42.1230160395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_02_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。今年も一緒に頂点を\n見据えて頑張りましょう\nしっかりマネジメントを\nお願いしますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. Let's aim for the top together this year.\nPlease manage us well!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.3333333333,
      "endTime": 49.6572791418,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_02_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "うんうん、トップアイドル\n目指して頑張ろー！！\nそれじゃ改めまして！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah yeah‚ let's work hard to become top idols!\nSo‚ once again!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.8666666667,
      "endTime": 56.500557339100006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_02_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "せーの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "On the count of three!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.6666666667,
      "endTime": 58.159433094700006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ハッピーニューイヤー！！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Happy New Year!!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.3666666667,
      "endTime": 60.4,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}